file.name: header-cookie-body-params.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0"
info:
  title: Simple
paths:
  /test:
    post:
      responses:
        200:
          description: 200 OK
      parameters:
        - name: key
          schema:
            type: integer
          required: false
          in: header
        - name: min_date
          schema:
            type: string
          required: true
          in: header
          format: date
        - in: cookie
          name: csrftoken
          schema:
            type: string
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/SimpleObj'
components:
  schemas:
    SimpleObj:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
